@base = https://endpoints.hckr.mx/proxys

# ──── CUSTOM PROXY ────
# x-proxy-target: full URL (path + query included) to forward the request to

### Custom proxy — GET request
GET {{base}}/custom
x-proxy-target: https://endpoints.hckr.mx/starfish/otp

### Custom proxy — POST request
POST {{base}}/custom
x-proxy-target: https://api.example.com/users?active=true
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "dan"
}

# ──── METEO PROXY ────
# Transparent proxy to https://api.open-meteo.com — passes path + query through

### Get weather forecast (proxied to open-meteo.com)
GET {{base}}/meteo/v1/forecast?latitude=19.43&longitude=-99.13&current=temperature_2m,wind_speed_10m
